description:
Danny talks about the gay representation in Pixar's LUCA, then welcomes Hannah Einbinder who plays Ava in Hacks on HBO Max to talk about the season, working with Jean Smart, season 2, the Selena Gomez scene, and much more!


Hannah Einbinder Interview: 9:00ish
